9. Nf3 d6 10. Nd2 Ba6 11. e3 Nd7 12. Bxc4 Bg7 $132 {[%cal Ga8b8,Gb8b2,Gd7e5]
with decent chances to seize the initiative.}) ({simply wrong is} 5. Bh4 $2 {
, which runs into} g5 6. Bg3 Bg7 {[%cal Gg7b2,Gd8a5]} 7. Nd2 Qa5 $17) 5... Qa5+
