8. Qd3) 7. dxe6 (7. Nc3 {is a major alternative, the position strongly
resembles the 5.b6 e6 variation:} Nxd5 ({Black can prefer} 7... exd5 8. Nxd5 {
and then choose between transposition or to try} Bb7 {, when he should be
