each simplification. Black seems in order with the alternative capture after a
preliminary bishop check as well.} Bxd6 26. Kb1 (26. Qxe6+ Kg7 27. Kb1 Rfe8 28.
Qxe8 Rxe8 29. Rxe8 Qc5 $132) 26... Kg7 27. h4 Bc7 $11 *

